WEBVTT

06:05.430 --> 06:08.630 line:80%
Does he know whether the Marquis of Wu'an
is alive or dead?

06:09.430 --> 06:11.230 line:80%
Th-The Marquis of Wu'an is dead?

06:11.400 --> 06:12.230 line:80%
Is that true?

06:12.230 --> 06:13.430 line:80%
The Marquis of Wu'an?

06:13.670 --> 06:16.910 line:80%
-Listen. Isn't that what people say?
-The Marquis of Wu'an really died.
